Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART1===========
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.64,0:01:37.04,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆的日本童话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.00,0:01:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真少
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.49,0:01:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年给的特别少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.40,0:01:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是他们影向到我的份了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.79,0:01:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是什么东西嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.44,0:01:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好少喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.19,0:02:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 不依靠别人过不了好年的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.32,0:02:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿到这么多钱 我还是头一回呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.24,0:02:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邀请达令一起去吃饭、喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.20,0:02:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,享受只有两人的快乐年吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.40,0:02:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南无阿弥陀佛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.92,0:02:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？没人出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.39,0:02:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 这年头人都无法得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没法子 那么只好我自已进去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.52,0:02:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有话要告诉你们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.87,0:02:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是在这时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.91,0:02:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们应该没忘了我对你们的恩惠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.71,0:02:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩惠？是什么东西呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.53,0:02:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是就是因为有我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.91,0:02:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们才能拿到压岁钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.43,0:02:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然我不要你们全部的红包
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.45,0:02:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一些的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.61,0:02:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.86,0:02:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好不容易收到的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.20,0:02:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫我送你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没说要你们送我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是叫你们以报恩之意还我一些而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.67,0:02:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你才没什么感恩之意呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.22,0:02:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.12,0:02:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你可有满怀的感谢之意哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.39,0:03:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！这样的呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.31,0:03:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真能了解我的感受呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.84,0:03:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我的压岁钱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.23,0:03:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过个只有两人的快乐新年吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.93,0:03:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是呀！用你的压岁钱…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.68,0:03:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想给达令你买礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后一起去餐厅吃饭 喝茶…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.25,0:03:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是十分愉快啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.84,0:03:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么呀！你！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.16,0:03:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也带我一起去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.29,0:03:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对一个连感恩都不懂的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.00,0:03:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门儿都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.60,0:03:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 小天有点可怜…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.35,0:03:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也带我一起去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这小子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.98,0:03:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是寄宿在此的人\N还将收到的压岁钱给独吞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我的就是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.32,0:03:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人甭想拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.21,0:03:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还想破坏我们的约会？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.98,0:04:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带我去是理所当然的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.16,0:04:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于我的出现 未使各位受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也真庆幸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.71,0:04:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的谈话我都听见了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就交给我好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.54,0:04:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.72,0:04:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好孩子要午睡才会长大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.30,0:04:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说故事 让心情放松
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要到餐厅吃饭的事 是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心 放心 快点说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.78,0:04:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从前从前 有一个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一个地方 是哪里呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.60,0:04:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住着老公公和老婆婆…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.70,0:04:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为这个故事我就会听吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一只麻雀也住在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.16,0:04:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三人感情融洽的生活着…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去河边洗衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.97,0:05:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老头子呀！你先熬浆糊哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心 交给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小麻雀呀！熬个浆糊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆说叫爷爷你熬的呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.23,0:05:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要稍为出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.70,0:05:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就代我熬一下？不成呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.83,0:05:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要偷懒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.44,0:05:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是又要去找小姑娘了呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.20,0:05:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的收成不好 又要养麻雀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知能不能过冬呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答应熬浆糊了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.63,0:05:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:06:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘你在哪儿呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.71,0:06:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷他呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.41,0:06:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都去找小姑娘的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.35,0:06:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬天可难过了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法过冬…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好味道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.70,0:06:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法过冬…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.79,0:06:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行 吃了就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.38,0:06:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果无法过冬 那…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅花开了花吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午饭还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.50,0:06:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小麻雀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浆糊熬好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 熬好了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那儿呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在仓库的一角呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:07:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.80,0:07:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在外面的一角呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.59,0:07:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在客厅的一角呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.10,0:07:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小麻雀 我怎么找也没有呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.50,0:07:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事 好好的找一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.48,0:07:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 被你吃掉了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.45,0:07:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.00,0:07:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你那圆圆鼓起的肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.60,0:07:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子本来就圆圆鼓鼓的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舌、舌头 危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷为了不让麻雀再偷吃浆糊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以将麻雀的舌头给剪掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:08:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.91,0:08:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？没看而小麻雀 跑哪儿去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.08,0:08:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,费心熬好的浆糊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全被小麻雀那家伙偷吃光了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是给他一点教训
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他的舌头给剪了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.15,0:08:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是胡乱作为呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那么疼那只麻雀 而你却…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.97,0:08:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在河边捡到这粒桃子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正想三人好好分享一番呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.95,0:08:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 既然是在河边捡到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.14,0:08:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉上好像小了一点呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.05,0:08:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有在童话中才有大桃子啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.30,0:08:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱的小孩子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.17,0:08:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在哪看过这小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.95,0:08:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能看过嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮他取个名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.00,0:09:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有十公分左右 就叫天法师吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他是从桃子里冒出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得桃太郎这名字比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.10,0:09:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么各取其中就叫一寸桃太郎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对没有孩子的二老而言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.55,0:09:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一寸桃太郎真是有如掌上之宝呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.57,0:09:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二老非常疼爱他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.77,0:09:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭啊、鱼啊、田里的青菜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.35,0:09:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都给他吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.79,0:09:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 看来好像是不够吃似的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.32,0:09:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是 去捉免子…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捉白痴的果子狸…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说就连狐狸都吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连体格庞大的大熊也不放过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后终究塞进了一寸桃太郎的胃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 那完全成为养分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.68,0:09:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日渐强壮高大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.15,0:10:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么能吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将来一定会成为有用之人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论他是否能成为有用之人\N我可是变得一文不值了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好饿啊！老太婆呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.87,0:10:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一带已没什么食物了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,0:10:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在这种乡下没什么剌激
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.26,0:10:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.59,0:10:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奉神喻而来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.22,0:10:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神喻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.72,0:10:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了指点你明途而来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.04,0:10:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那 告诉我那神喻呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会告诉你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.93,0:10:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 可不是免费的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别小气 快说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.43,0:10:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道 我想知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.35,0:10:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等 你在干什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.05,0:10:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要尊重神明呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.99,0:10:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是好事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想不想去京城呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.22,0:11:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京城？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.16,0:11:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.23,0:11:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花般美丽的京城 梦般似的京城 向往的京城
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.76,0:11:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我有上了年纪的双亲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.35,0:11:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护我免于风雨侵袭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.25,0:11:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,费心养育我的老公公和老婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放置二老于此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而一人到京城享受消遥的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.21,0:11:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这实在太不孝顺了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.80,0:11:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将那两老留在此地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.60,0:11:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.48,0:11:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什么坏事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻找我的梦想 我办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.95,0:11:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双亲不会原谅我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.46,0:11:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那可不是吃萝葡饭的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.29,0:11:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到处都有好吃的东西喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由美丽小姑娘送来的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要像你这气度男子在街上着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:12:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.10,0:12:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被这么说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.35,0:12:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可惜呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.48,0:12:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将大好人生浪费在这小村庄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.42,0:12:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会只有一次哟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.03,0:12:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不愿看到父母亲悲伤的神情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这是小孩旅行的权利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.45,0:12:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对呀！拿出勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.87,0:12:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.45,0:12:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去梦幻京城怎能断送于父母亲之手呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.20,0:12:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.75,0:12:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 在这里受了神喻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.94,0:12:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能留在这种地方过一生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去京城
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.52,0:12:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.43,0:12:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管别人说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.23,0:13:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已决定要去京城了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART2===========
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京城真的住着妖怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.58,0:13:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 杀掉大妖怪的话就能得到宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.58,0:13:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们等着你的好消息哟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一寸桃太郎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.97,0:13:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 根据神喻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.22,0:13:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京城是个美丽小姑娘的集合地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.17,0:13:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且很快乐的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？根据神喻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.31,0:13:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有数不尽的美丽小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.65,0:13:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在京城里？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.68,0:13:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在那胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在京城的是大妖怪呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.76,0:13:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有许多宝物的大妖怪呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.40,0:13:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会错的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.76,0:13:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他说到处都有好吃的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.02,0:13:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫殿里还住着美丽的公主呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.71,0:13:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个美丽的老太婆就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:13:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去杀了大妖怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.78,0:14:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来时 别忘了宝物哟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好保重身体喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.74,0:14:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老太婆你的感受我完全了解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是担心一寸桃太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.79,0:14:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人去对付那大妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.75,0:14:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 现在挽留他也来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.37,0:14:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.51,0:14:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再多说了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.74,0:14:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 刚说的可是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀！是呀！真是孝顺的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.69,0:14:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们父子俩鬼鬼崇崇地说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.60,0:14:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是在商量如何才能\N让你高枕无忧的等宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？那么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.79,0:14:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？要去看小姑娘 公主的糟老头子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此途中 你二人就能消遥自在了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别妄想了！你敢！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.65,0:14:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保重了 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心哟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.38,0:14:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.48,0:15:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京城有好多美丽的小姑娘哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.10,0:15:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样又只剩下我们两人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.05,0:15:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像又回到新婚时期似的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.45,0:15:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人来打扰又可以快活一番
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.51,0:15:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.80,0:15:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都上了年纪 还有什么新婚气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一道走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.55,0:15:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 你这背叛者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.68,0:15:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…喜欢…年轻的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.56,0:15:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我一人放在家里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.44,0:15:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 你给我记住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京城真有美丽的小姑娘吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.38,0:15:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真期待！真期待！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这种身体的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.79,0:15:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得想办法变年轻才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.77,0:16:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说这附近有一家专门要造返老还童的药
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.80,0:16:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.50,0:16:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我变年轻的药
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.19,0:16:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到哪种程度的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.55,0:16:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能受小姑娘欢迎的年轻程度就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.27,0:16:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.35,0:16:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就不算你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就别忘记这张脸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.07,0:16:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在哪儿见过似的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.32,0:16:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间一过就会复原状的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.70,0:16:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可没听说有这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,童话还真是不可相信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.87,0:16:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好凭自己的力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.97,0:16:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！猫儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.09,0:16:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如不想妨碍我伟大的命运就滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.88,0:17:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙把我当成傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.70,0:17:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！猫儿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.93,0:17:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我打一仗决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.74,0:17:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很厉害的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.04,0:17:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不怕 看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别躲了 臭猫 死猫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而被奇怪的家伙给…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.59,0:17:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变年轻真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过就是没什么现代感
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样 一人不如二人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.72,0:17:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个部下就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.20,0:17:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫儿呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要吃黄米饭团呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.40,0:17:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别客气 要不要吃呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧 吃了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！猫儿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完后 要不要做我的部下呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.93,0:17:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想吃的话就跟我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是京城！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.72,0:18:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是神喻所说的京城
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.26,0:18:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是所谓的京城呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知有没有小姑娘呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.16,0:18:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！有嘛！有嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.68,0:18:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱的小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.48,0:18:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美丽的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.63,0:18:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.49,0:18:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.08,0:18:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能打败骚扰京城的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.99,0:18:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有权利向公主求婚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然有大妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.32,0:18:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过能和公主结婚的话 真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.00,0:18:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主 安心睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.49,0:18:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会好好保护公主的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.88,0:18:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别被乱事吓昏了头脑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而做出下流的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.67,0:19:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此鬼怪还要厉害呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道就没有可依靠的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.90,0:19:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到何时才会出现\N强壮的男子来解救可怜的我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.49,0:19:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来救你了公主
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.58,0:19:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是唯一能拯救公主的好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.67,0:19:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这人山人海的是干嘛呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.46,0:19:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么大东西呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.70,0:19:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别挡路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.37,0:19:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.20,0:19:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是公主的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.51,0:20:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要打败它 就能和公主结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.45,0:20:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有宝物 一生都无忧无虑了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可要上了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！猫儿 我俩赶紧去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.60,0:20:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.81,0:20:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.00,0:20:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主 我来救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.03,0:20:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大妖怪 来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.54,0:20:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.00,0:20:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球上已没有强壮的男人了么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.92,0:20:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.00,0:21:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！公主被…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.01,0:21:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捉走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.00,0:21:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 等等 别逃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.70,0:21:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.26,0:21:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都是兔子舞 烦都烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.00,0:21:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 在这 在这
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.10,0:21:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变小了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.72,0:21:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.50,0:21:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公王 我们来救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.78,0:21:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来救你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.34,0:21:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 大家可加油了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.19,0:22:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.93,0:22:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.10,0:22:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.20,0:22:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 正如童话一样 变大了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.40,0:22:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 两人都变得高大强壮了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.02,0:22:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主 可别忘了我哟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.89,0:22:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不高大强壮的 我讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.77,0:22:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啦！公主
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.14,0:22:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打败大妖怪后…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.36,0:22:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前先和公主…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.61,0:22:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球人真是缠人呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.29,0:22:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下 公主
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.91,0:23:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！药效退了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.47,0:23:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真累
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.00,0:23:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故事就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.61,0:23:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说餐厅的佳肴 我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.80,0:23:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡着了 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========预告===========
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.50,0:23:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中有着憧憬的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.75,0:23:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直等到今天的龙之介
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.82,0:23:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷带着积蓄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.81,0:23:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑到内衣专卖店
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.26,0:23:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想买一件胸罩穿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.14,0:24:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多年的愿望 是否能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.35,0:24:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之介的女人心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.43,0:24:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.19,0:24:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪亮发光 向往的胸罩
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.17,0:24:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========OP===========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.22,0:00:17.06,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当都市皆沉静之时 男人将成为天蝎座
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.31,0:00:24.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人将成为处女座 跳吧 跳舞 跳舞 在夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.48,0:00:31.64,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,触动内心的指头 两人技巧地滑动着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.64,0:00:38.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到何时才会出现强壮的男子\N来解救可怜的我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.55,0:00:45.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抛开一切用力抱紧 并且说不让你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.75,0:00:52.38,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今夜一定只有两人独处 并沉溺于亲吻之中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.63,0:00:59.51,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 我的眼中 映着你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.67,0:01:07.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 你的眼中 我是多么美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.46,0:01:14.46,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霎时燃烬的夜晚 男人将化为星尘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.79,0:01:21.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人将化成流星 跳吧 跳舞 跳舞 舞星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.43,0:01:29.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳吧 跳舞 跳舞 舞星 跳吧 跳舞 跳舞 舞星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========ED===========
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.27,0:24:24.31,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄昏的街道是 薄薄地闪耀着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.43,0:24:31.60,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何男人也 看来更加温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.81,0:24:38.12,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犹豫的心胸 让其诱惑了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.12,0:24:43.28,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使坠入情网 那也只是一时性地
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.30,0:24:50.78,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的是 只有你一人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.96,0:24:57.02,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论何时都能投入怀抱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.33,0:25:03.33,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回头之后你已不在
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.65,0:25:09.36,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法发泄的心留存在此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.11,0:25:17.23,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱经常是两人的东西 梦是一个 更爱我一些
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.48,0:25:23.28,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 恋爱是两人的东西 没有终了的 更爱我一些
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.82,0:25:29.74,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啦… 啦… 啦… 啦… 啦… 啦… 爱我 更爱我一些
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.18,0:25:35.57,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}爱我 更爱我一些 爱我 更爱我一些

